OL,3,CIceland boss offers job to man sacked
OL,4,Cby Waitrose for confronting shoplifter
OL,6,FA retail worker sacked from Waitrose
OL,7,Ffor confronting a shoplifter has been
OL,8,Foffered a job by the boss of Iceland.
OL,10,FWalker Smith, 54, was dismissed by
OL,11,FWaitrose two days after confronting a
OL,12,Fshoplifter who was attempting to steal
OL,13,Fa bag of Easter eggs, leading to a
OL,14,Fbrief struggle before the shoplifter
OL,15,Ffled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
