OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775635511
OL,3,CIceland boss offers job to man sacked
OL,4,Cby Waitrose for confronting shoplifter
OL,6,FLord Richard Walker, executive
OL,7,Fchairman of Iceland and the
OL,8,Fgovernment's cost-of-living champion,
OL,9,Fsaid in a LinkedIn post on Monday
OL,10,Fevening: "You're welcome to a job with
OL,11,Fus. We even share the same name..." in
OL,12,Fresponse to an article detailing Mr
OL,13,FSmith's sacking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
