CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775635511
OL,3,CIceland boss offers job to man sacked
OL,4,Cby Waitrose for confronting shoplifter
OL,6,FMr Smith, who had worked at the
OL,7,Fretailer's Clapham Junction branch for
OL,8,F17 years, told the media he regretted
OL,9,Fhis actions, but had been driven to
OL,10,Fintervene after watching thefts at the
OL,11,Fstore "every hour of every day for the
OL,12,Flast five years" and not being allowed
OL,13,Fto do anything.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
