PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775635511
OL,3,CIceland boss offers job to man sacked
OL,4,Cby Waitrose for confronting shoplifter
OL,6,FIt comes after shadow home secretary
OL,7,FChris Philp said Waitrose had acted
OL,8,F"disgracefully" by sacking Mr Smith.
OL,10,FIn a letter to Waitrose managing
OL,11,Fdirector Tom Denyard, posted on social
OL,12,Fmedia, Philp called for Mr Smith to be
OL,13,Freinstated and paid a bonus "for his
OL,14,Fbravery and initiative".
OL,16,FHe said: "Staff safety must come first.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]uD@]OUvD@WO]xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775635511
OL,3,CIceland boss offers job to man sacked
OL,4,Cby Waitrose for confronting shoplifter
OL,6,F"But dismissing a long-serving
OL,7,Femployee in these circumstances sends
OL,8,Fentirely the wrong message. It
OL,9,Fpenalises those who act, while
OL,10,Foffenders are left unchecked."
OL,12,FThe incident comes as shoplifting
OL,13,Fcases continue to increase, with
OL,14,Foffences increasing 5% in the year to
OL,15,FSeptember 2025, according to the
OL,16,Flatest figures.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
