PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775635511
OL,3,CIceland boss offers job to man sacked
OL,4,Cby Waitrose for confronting shoplifter
OL,6,FWaitrose has said that the reporting
OL,7,Fof Mr Smith's case, based on an
OL,8,Finterview with The Guardian, does not
OL,9,Fcover the "full facts of the
OL,10,Fsituation".
OL,12,FThe supermarket chain also said the
OL,13,F"safety and security" of their workers
OL,14,Fand customers is the reason they have
OL,15,Fpolicies in place to stop actions like
OL,16,Fthose of Mr Smith.
OL,18,FWaitrose said it would not discuss Mr
OL,19,FSmith's case specifically, but added
OL,20,Fthe "correct process" was followed,
OL,21,Fincluding an appeals procedure.
OL,26,@qD@KOUrD@JO]uD@AOUuD@UO]|D@EOU|D@UO]
